T at all about suicide or depression.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2423470/extras/e085d9effad930c6681d377e38841191.avif?t=1737451209\" width=568 height=364 /></span>",
